Dear Mr John Nash,

The Az 1 TeamCoord at Org A has invited you to access the medical information of Mrs Bea Patient so you can help manage their health.

Message from The Az 1 TeamCoord

Please consider being my carer

To accept this invitation, click this link:

http://pkb-frontend-10/registerPatientStart.action?uid=2154&temp=lDrK9Wy3UG

Questions?
  1. Is this secure? Patients Know Best is GDPR-compliant for European patients and HIPAA-compliant for US ones. The UK site is part of the NHS secure network (N3), so it is already built to NHS security standards and approved for usage with any NHS computer.
  2. Do I have to register with the web site? Yes, but registration is free and fast. Please click this link: http://pkb-frontend-10/registerPatientStart.action?uid=2154&temp=lDrK9Wy3UG
  3. What happens after I register? You can access the records of Mrs Bea Patient to use Patients Know Best together securely.

You are receiving this notification because you have been invited as a carer. Once registered, log in and review the people you care for by following this link: "http://pkb-frontend-10/patient/myDependents.action?tab=invitations&subTab=dependents"

Please do not reply to this email; this address is not monitored.

Yours,

Patients Know Best Help Team
